channel.title: Road to 45 dung & 40k tokens
channel.description: Hey guys i am currently going for 45 dung maybe even 50 trying to get 40k tokens i really need the gravite bow for pking... it's be nice to know i had all of your guy's support.. :) [IMG]http://i1239.photobucket.com/albums/ff502/codyskate5021/gravitebowupdate1.jpg[/img]

item.title: Road to 45 dung & 40k tokens
item.dc:creator: @judostar1 judostar1
item.description:
@judostar1 wrote:

[quote=“Phaze One, post:5, topic:422041”][quote author=codyskate5021 link=topic=524722.msg3819211#msg3819211 date=1321631914]

The accumulation of 40k tokens occurs at 64 dungeoneering.

this is just my range pure onmy main i got it at about 48 dung because i only did complexity 6 on floors 6-8 when they were unlocked getting me about 200 tokens a round when i solo the dungeons
[/quote]

40k tokens = A minimum of 400,000 xp.[/quote]

not nessarly, you do get more then 100 every dung. But yes. 400k exp is req for 40k tokens min.
